programme.desc: Lancashire Lightning v Worcestershire Rapids. Coverage of the North Division clash, which takes place at Old Trafford. Lancashire - along with Hampshire and Surrey - have reached the most Finals Days in the competition's history, having appeared six times. The Rapids have never made it to Finals Day, having been beaten in five quarter-finals over the years
